{"parse":{"title":"Firefin Snapper","pageid":15670,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||5}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_MonsterHead_01\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=6359\n|ilvl=25\n|name=Firefin Snapper}}</onlyinclude>\n\n'''Firefin Snapper''' is obtained by [[fishing]] and is a component in [[Fire Oil]] (made with [[Alchemy]]). Fishing for Firefin Snapper requires [[Fishing_locations#Fishing_skill_levels_by_zone|(fourth tier)]] fishing skill-level of 130 (or 225 to ensure a catch). Firefin Snapper can be fished straight from the water or also from an Oil Spill [[Fishing#Schools_of_Fish|School]]. \n\n==Source==\nThis fish can be caught in coastal waters in the below zones, and the lakes of [[Stonetalon Mountains]].  These zones have at least a minimum fishing skill of 55 required. Some Listed Zones may have higher minimum fishing skill level:\n*[[Arathi Highlands]]\n*[[Ashenvale]]\n*[[Azshara]]\n*[[Booty Bay]] \n*[[Desolace]] \n*[[Dustwallow Marsh]]\n*[[Feralas]]\n*[[Hillsbrad Foothills]]\n*[[The Hinterlands]]\n*[[Stranglethorn Vale]]\n*[[Tanaris]]\n*[[Wetlands]]\n\n==Firefin Snapper as an ingredient==\n\n=== Alchemy ===\n*[[Fire Oil]]\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft ingredient items]]\n\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6359}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/firefin_snapper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft alchemy ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:Alchemy Materials]]"}}}